defaultQ1 default&#xa0; 
defaultChair:default Good afternoon and welcome.  Thank you very much for coming in to share your experiences of 
defaultBurma
default and your thoughts about where it might be heading.  As you know, the Committee is heading out there next week, and two of us have actually been out with the Speaker’s group in July.  We are looking at democracy and development, and the link between the two, given the way things have changed.  I just wondered, first of all, for the record, if you could introduce yourselves and your organisation.  
