defaultLondon
default here, but I lived and worked in 
defaultMyanmar
default, in 
defaultBurma
default, between 2008 and 2011, originally managing the response to Cyclone Nargis.
defaultChris White:default Before we start, can I just, for the record, express an interest?  I had a relationship with Cord, having visited 
defaultChad
